HEADWORD: Ambary hemp
<hw>Ambary hemp</hw> }</mhw>. <ety>[Hind. <ets>amb⟦amac⟧r⟦amac⟧</ets>,
<ets>amb⟦amac⟧r⟦imac⟧</ets>.]</ety> <def>A valuable East Indian fiber
